SCHEMA: models/model_type.schema
schema_id: dominium.schema.models.model_type
schema_version: 1.0.0
stability: core

PURPOSE:
- Declare reusable constitutive model type families and parameter schemas.

REQUIRED SHAPE:
record model_type
  required:
    - schema_version: semver
    - model_type_id: id
    - description: text
    - parameter_schema_id: id
    - extensions: map

INVARIANTS:
- Type IDs are stable and registry-driven.
- Parameter schema references are declarative and deterministic.
